                     <interp inst="t18280911-338-person1839" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker. I took in this watch from some man; I do not know who.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280911-338-person1840">
                  THOMAS 
